modcontent-installprompt =
    Combined Arms requires artwork and audio from the original games.

    Quick Install will automatically download this content (without music\nor videos) from a mirror of the 2008 Command & Conquer/Red Alert
    freeware release.

    Advanced Install allows you to install music and other content,
    which may require original game installations or discs.

    You can also install this additional content later via the main menu.
modcontent-header =
